5. Orchestrator Interface

orchestrator.py

run()
CLI entry point.  
Routes modes → modules.

Modes
- Single‑universe:  
  dashboard, replay, heatmap, glyph, glyph_anim, operators, delta3
- Dual‑universe:  
  dashboardmulti, phaselock, field, fused, fusedanim, instrument, replaymulti
- Multi‑universe:  
  compare

